l-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-backs-far-right-demand-to-limit-arab-israeli-worshipers-at-al-aqsa-in-ramadan/0000018d-bd60-dc8c-a3df-ff75cc820000</guid></item><item><title>拉马拉呼吁美国支持巴勒斯坦权力机构成为联合国会员国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/ramallah-calls-on-u-s-to-back-palestinian-authority-as-un-member-state/0000018d-bda8-dc8c-a3df-ffbd776d0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦权力机构的一名高级官员告诉《国土报》，国际社会在宣布两国解决方案的同时，还应该采取行动来证明其严肃性。巴勒斯坦权力机构总理表示，只要哈马斯接受“先决条件”，它准备与哈马斯合作</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 19:54:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/ramallah-calls-on-u-s-to-back-palestinian-authority-as-un-member-state/0000018d-bda8-dc8c-a3df-ffbd776d0000</guid></item><item><title>讲述以色列从第二次起义到有史以来最严重的加沙战争的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/telling-israels-story-from-the-second-intifada-to-its-worst-ever-gaza-war/0000018d-bc61-dd5e-a59d-fdf3f1d80000</link><description>以色列年度当地见证展览的最佳照片已汇集在一本书中。展览创始人 Dana Wohlfeiler-Lalkin 带我们经历个人和国家之旅</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:50:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/telling-israels-story-from-the-second-intifada-to-its-worst-ever-gaza-war/0000018d-bc61-dd5e-a59d-fdf3f1d80000</guid></item><item><title>历史性胜利：以色列游泳运动员在多哈世锦赛上获得银牌，遭到嘘声</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-swimmer-takes-silver-medal-booed-at-doha-world-championships/0000018d-bd78-dd5e-a59d-fdfa980b0000</link><description>“我很高兴来到这里，”阿纳斯塔西娅·戈尔本科说道，尽管卡塔尔首都的当地观众发出了嘘声。周日，她成为第一位在同一届世锦赛上两次闯入个人决赛的以色列人，在预赛中获得第五名</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 18:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israel-swimmer-takes-silver-medal-booed-at-doha-world-championships/0000018d-bd78-dd5e-a59d-fdfa980b0000</guid></i