remium/company-of-sanctioned-israeli-settler-registered-under-his-brother-amid-restrictions/0000018d-bc42-dc8c-a3df-fe7719280000</guid></item><item><title>在花费数年时间使以色列两极分化之后，内塔尼亚胡将团结作为武器来对抗异见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/after-spending-years-polarizing-israel-netanyahu-uses-unity-as-a-weapon-against-dissent/0000018d-bc12-df10-a99f-bff397fe0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡曾经证明，对他来说，战争为另一场政治运动提供了一个平台，其特点是所有熟悉的特征：谎言、煽动、煽动激情和转移注意力</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 13:26:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/after-spending-years-polarizing-israel-netanyahu-uses-unity-as-a-weapon-against-dissent/0000018d-bc12-df10-a99f-bff397fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部长取消除“英雄主义”之外的所有以色列奖奖项类别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-cancels-all-israel-prize-awards-categories-except-for-heroism/0000018d-bbfe-dd5e-a59d-fffe21930000</link><description>今年的以色列奖将不会颁发传统的人文、科学和文化类别，而只会颁发一个类别，其中六名获奖者“在 10 月 7 日发生的可怕危机后为国家的复苏做出了贡献”</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 12:52:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-education-minister-cancels-all-israel-prize-awards-categories-except-for-heroism/0000018d-bbfe-dd5e-a59d-fffe21930000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔的赚钱机器为其全球影响力铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/qatars-money-machine-smooths-its-path-to-global-influence/0000018d-ad18-d30f-a39f-ff797e3b0000</link><description>这个小酋长国为包括哈马斯在内的伊斯兰恐怖组织提供资金，并控制了美国在核技术、网络安全和人工智能方面的战略资产。我们是否应该担心这一切最终都会落入伊朗手中？</description><pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 12:44:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-02-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/qatars-money-machine-smooths-its-path-to-global-influence/0000018d-ad18-d30f-a39f-ff797e3b0000</guid></item><it